<emphasis bold="true" box="[729,904,2186,2219]" pageId="197" pageNumber="476">Distribution.</emphasis>
SE Peru through SW Bolivia and extreme NE Chile to NW 
<taxonomicName box="[1153,1296,2226,2259]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Argentina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="197" pageNumber="476" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Argentina</taxonomicName>
